Package: Rtwobitlib
Title: 2bit C library from the UCSC Genome Browser wrapped in an R package
Description: The package contains a copy of a small subset of the
	UCSC Genome Browser source code repository located at
	https://github.com/ucscGenomeBrowser/kent/
	Only the .c and .h files related to manipulation of files in the 2bit
	format are included. Note that the package is primarily useful to
	developers of other R packages who wish to use the 2bit C library in
	their own C code.
biocViews: Infrastructure, DataImport, GenomeAssemby
Version: 0.0.1
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
